{
  "stem": "11000.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "So then, we were lined up after we had the second piece of bread, and we were told that the factory is gonna be closed, and they're going to move us into Germany.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "We had to go to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "We would be transferred to a-- a German factory into Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "We went.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "Train never arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "They said the railroad tracks were damaged or bombed, and the train never came.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "I don't know how long we were there waiting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then, they decided we can't go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We should march into Germany as far as we get.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had combined the other two Gleiwitz camps with us, so there were six-- about 6,000 of us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, we started to march, and this was in January '45.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Winters in that part of the country are very severe, and this was a lot of snow, a lot of ice, a lot of cold.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we just marched, and you came to the point where you couldn't march anymore.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Those who were unable to continue, they were just shot alongside the road and just left there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think the third day we marched, and during the night, we were put up in a-- it used to be a French prisoner of war camp, which had been vacated-- was empty.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they put us into those barracks just for the night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next morning, we were supposed to go on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the time where we really-- the five of us, we sat there and said look, we just can't.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just-- you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't-- physically, you couldn't do it, and we saw what happened to the ones that-- on the way, so we decided we're not gonna go.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We're gonna stay here.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
